high_descs: turn right and head towards the coffee maker
pick up the mug from the coffee maker
turn around and head for the sink
rinse the mug in the sink
turn around and head back to the coffee maker
place the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: place a clean mug in the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn to face the coffee maker.
Pick the cup up from under the coffee maker.
GO to the right and the take another right to stand in front of the sink.
Put the mug in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the mug up.
Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the coffee maker.
Put the cup down under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug under a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right to face the counter with the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug at the coffee maker.
Turn left, go forward, turn right to go to the sink.
Clean the mug in the sink.
Turn around, go straight, turn left, go forward, then turn right to return to the coffee maker.
Place the mug at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug at the coffee maker.
